{"tid":1474481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記者會：經濟下滑因暴力事件是將責任推向示威者","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:55:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcf6b83c5122506c938abba35d5a8895ff9f102","tid":1474481,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1474850_1_20190815154616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1474850_1_20190815154616.jpg&h=1983c4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由市民組成的民間記者會第四度舉行，發言人認為，政府在星期一的跨部門記者會把經濟下滑是因為近期暴力事件導致，是將把責任推向示威者。<br />\n<br />\n發言人周先生舉例，在721元朗事件後的一星期內對本港發出旅遊警示的國家增加了6個。而根據旅遊發展局數字，去年同期訪港旅客在1月份至6月份錄得雙位數升幅，直到7月下旬跌近3成。<br />\n<br />\n另外，周先生認為，警方在記者會播放的片段並非事實的全部，是刻意向公眾展示部份片段。他亦指出有另一些網上片段，顯示示威者是想保護一名可能會被警方帶走的女士，才發生及後的事情。<br />\n<br />\n周先生表示，民陣將舉行的是和理非遊行，如警方不批出不反對通知書的做法，是有違《基本法》保障的遊行集會自由。"},{"pid":"cee14b49b17dd45c8d368c9a7cfda03f27faae08","tid":1474481,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474850-20190815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474850-20190815.htm&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=12e960f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474850-20190815.htm&h=ad9bdf9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474850-20190815.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3cd754630b8d9c5b8c3c8f2c31f133f40846772d","tid":1474481,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s=